湖北22名误食消毒片的村民，“已无大碍”。
Hubei 22 people who mistakenly eat disinfectant film villagers, "there is no harm."
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
央视新闻央视新闻消息，黄梅县黄梅镇人民政府3月1日发布消息称：2月28日上午9时30分左右，黄梅镇向窑村一组村民14户22人误食镇疫情防控指挥部下发的二氧化氯环境消毒片（俗称“泡腾片”），剂量1粒/人，后紧急送往县人民医院救治。
Huangmei Township People's Government of Huangmei County on February 28 at 9: 30 am, Huangmei township to a group of 14 villagers misfeed the chlorine dioxide environmental disinfection tablets (commonly known as "bubble Tablets") issued by the township epidemic prevention and control command, a dose of 1 / person, and then rushed to the county People's Hospital for treatment.
据悉，22人中有6人在吞服时感觉不适，当时吐出。
Six of the 22 people were said to have vomited while swallowing.
目前22人经治疗已无大碍。
Twenty-two people are currently receiving treatment without major problems.
Play澎湃新闻记者：魏凡 编辑：张琳 视频来源：相关人士、网络责任编辑：李蕊经查，2月25日，黄梅镇向各村社区发放防护物资时，均交代清楚了泡腾片的用途及使用方法，每粒泡腾片兑2公斤水，用于住户家中喷洒消毒。
