向窑村安排村妇女主任、会计罗晓红及网格员翟锦霞负责向各小组发放物资。
Arrangements were made for village women's director, accountant Xiaohong Zhai Jinxia and grid worker Zhai Jinxia to distribute materials to the teams.
27日15时许，罗晓红电话通知一组组长蒋建军到村委会领取一组防护物资，发放给村民，但电话中未告知蒋建军泡腾片的用途及使用方法。
At about 1500 hours on the 27th, Luo Xiaohong called a group leader Jiang Jianjun to collect a group of protective materials and distribute them to the villagers, but did not tell Jiang Jianjun what the use of the tablets would be and how they would be used.
蒋建军因在小组做防疫劝导工作，便电话通知该村志愿者蒋金雄到村委会领取。
Jiang Jianjun for the team to do vaccination advisory work, he called the village volunteers Jiang Jinxiong to collect.
于是蒋金雄到村委会从罗晓红处将一组防护物资领走。
Jiang Jinxiong then went to the village committee from Luo Xiaohong to take away a group of protective materials.
罗晓红向蒋金雄说明了泡腾片是兑水后用来消毒的，每家5粒。
Luo Xiaohong explained to Jiang Jinxiong that the effervescent tablets are used to disinfect water, 5 tablets per family.
蒋金雄在领到防护物资后，在一组村民蒋延安家中交给蒋建军。
Jiang Jinxiong after receiving protective materials, in a group of villagers Jiang Yenan home to Jiang Jianjun.
蒋金雄认为物资是蒋建军通知其从村委会领取的，应当清楚物资的用途及方法，便没有向蒋建军说明泡腾片的用途及使用方法。
Jiang Jinxiong thought that the materials were collected by Jiang Jianjun from the village committee. He should know the purpose and method of using the materials.
28日9时30分左右，黄梅县黄梅镇向窑村一组组长蒋建军带领该村志愿者余奇鳌、蒋带兵、蒋永新挨家挨户进行体温测试、登记、分发泡腾片时，蒋建军在未弄清泡腾片的用途及使用方法的情况下，自以为泡腾片是防治新冠病毒的药物，于是告知村民“每人一粒，吞服”，部分吞服了泡腾片的村民反映不适，蒋建军及时将发放的泡腾片收回。
When Jiang Jianjun led a group of volunteers from Huangmei county, Huangmei County, to lead a group of volunteers from the village, Yu Qiao, Jiang led troops, Jiang Yongxin to conduct house-to-house temperature testing, registration and distribution of bubble film.
得知此消息后，镇、村干部立即赶到现场，将吞服了泡腾片的村民送往县人民医院治疗。
After learning this news, the town, village cadres immediately rushed to the scene, will swallow bubble film villagers sent to the county people's hospital for treatment.
县委、县政府主要领导第一时间赶到医院，安排部署救治工作。
County Party committee, county government main leader hastens to the hospital the first time, arranges the deployment cure work.
县人民医院第一时间成立由党委书记、院长、业务院长、医疗股股长、消化内科主任、神经内科主任、心内科主任、心内科护士长等8人组成的救治专班。
County People's Hospital was first set up by the Party Secretary, President, Director of Operations, Head of Medical Unit, Head of Digestion, Director of Neurology, Head of Cardiology, Head of Cardiology and Head of Cardiology.
目前通过鸡蛋清+牛奶中和、胃液导流、输液补充能量、24小时监测仪监测，定期测温、检查等方式，入院22人身体状况稳定，没有生命危险，并安排病人家属进行照料，其中21人预计将于3月2日出院，另外1人由于年纪偏大、身体患有其他疾病，将继续留院观察治疗。
At present, through egg white + milk neutralization, gastric juice diversion, 24-hour monitoring instrument monitoring, regular temperature and examination, 22 hospitalized people are in stable condition, no risk to their lives, and arrangements for the care of patients' families, 21 of whom are expected to be discharged on 2 March, while another will remain in hospital for observation and treatment due to advanced age and other illnesses.
黄梅镇表示将举一反三，全面整改。
Huangmei Town said it would take a comprehensive overhaul.
严格防控物资发放使用管理，全面开展防控物资发放使用业务培训，在全镇范围内对发放的防控药品进行排查，做到消毒用品单独放置、村干部专人管理，在消毒用品包装上张贴名称及使用方法，确保防控消毒物资正确使用，安全使用。
We will strictly control the distribution and use of materials, conduct comprehensive training in the use of materials for prevention and control, conduct town-wide checks on the distribution of preventive and control drugs, ensure that disinfectant supplies are placed separately and that village cadres are specially assigned to manage them, and post their names and methods of use on the packaging of disinfectant supplies to ensure their proper use and safe use.
